---
import Layout from '../layouts/TaskRocketLayout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Aitha | The Modern Front Desk" description="Aitha captures missed calls, responds by text, gathers the right details, routes urgent issues, and starts workflows.">
  <div class="aitha-page">
    <section class="aitha-hero"><div class="container hero-inner"><div><div class="eyebrow">Powered by TaskRocket</div><h1>Your Modern Front Desk,<br/><em style="font-style:normal;color:#FF7A30">Always Ready.</em></h1><p class="lead">Aitha captures missed calls, responds by text, gathers the right details, routes urgent issues, and starts the workflows your business depends on, even when no one can pick up.</p><div class="actions"><a class="btn orange" href="/contact">Get a Free Workflow Review</a><a class="btn light" href="#how-it-works">See How It Works</a></div><p class="small">Built for small businesses · No call left unanswered · Customized to your workflow</p></div><div class="phone-stack"><div class="phone-card"><div class="label">Incoming call</div><h3>Missed call from a customer</h3><p>Customer needs help while your staff is already busy.</p></div><div class="phone-card featured"><div class="label">Aitha responding</div><div class="bubble aitha">Hi, this is the office. Sorry we missed your call. What can we help you with?</div><div class="bubble in">I have a leak and need someone to call me.</div><div class="bubble out">Thanks. Is water actively running or causing damage right now?</div></div><div class="phone-card"><div class="label">Workflow started</div><h3>Routed to the right person</h3><p>Urgency, details, and contact information are organized for your team.</p></div></div></div></section>
    <section class="section" id="problem"><div class="container grid2"><div><div class="eyebrow">The problem</div><h2>Your customers do not care that your office is busy.</h2><p class="lead">They expect a response. Aitha gives your business a clean front-desk layer for the calls and texts that usually slip through the cracks.</p></div><div class="card"><ul class="list"><li>Missed calls become lost opportunities.</li><li>After-hours messages get buried.</li><li>Urgent issues interrupt the wrong person.</li><li>Routine issues still need a record for regular business hours.</li></ul></div></div></section>
    <section class="section"><div class="container"><div class="eyebrow">What Aitha does</div><h2>From customer message to organized action.</h2><div class="grid"><div class="card solution-card"><h3>Missed call response</h3><p>Aitha can text a caller after a missed call and ask what they need.</p></div><div class="card solution-card"><h3>Text intake</h3><p>Aitha collects the right information and organizes the request.</p></div><div class="card solution-card"><h3>Urgency triage</h3><p>Aitha helps separate true emergency items from regular business-hour requests.</p></div><div class="card solution-card"><h3>Routing</h3><p>Aitha can notify a manager, vendor, technician, or staff member based on your rules.</p></div><div class="card solution-card"><h3>Records</h3><p>Each interaction can create a record so requests do not get forgotten.</p></div><div class="card solution-card"><h3>Workflow triggers</h3><p>Aitha can start forms, tasks, scheduling, CRM updates, and other automations.</p></div></div></div></section>
    <section class="section teal-section" id="how-it-works"><div class="container"><div class="eyebrow" style="color:#2DD4BF">How it works</div><h2>Aitha answers the gap between missed and handled.</h2><div class="grid"><div class="card dark-card"><h3>01 · Customer reaches out</h3><p>They call, text, or submit a request.</p></div><div class="card dark-card"><h3>02 · Aitha asks smart questions</h3><p>The conversation collects details and checks urgency.</p></div><div class="card dark-card"><h3>03 · The workflow moves</h3><p>Your team gets a record, alert, task, or next step.</p></div></div></div></section>
    <section class="section"><div class="container"><div class="eyebrow">Use cases</div><h2>Built for the work that normally lives in someone's head.</h2><div class="grid"><div class="card"><h3>Property management</h3><p>Tenant requests, maintenance triage, vendor routing, and records.</p></div><div class="card"><h3>Service businesses</h3><p>Missed calls, estimate requests, scheduling, and customer questions.</p></div><div class="card"><h3>Local offices</h3><p>Busy phones, repetitive intake, after-hours messages, and callback requests.</p></div></div></div></section>
    <section class="section"><div class="container"><div class="card" style="text-align:center"><h2>Let Aitha catch the next missed call before it becomes missed revenue.</h2><p class="lead" style="margin:auto auto 28px">Start with a TaskRocket workflow review and we will map where Aitha can support your business.</p><a class="btn orange" href="/contact">Get a Free Workflow Review</a></div></div></section>
  </div>
</Layout>
